abstract: The invention relates to the field of food packaging, and specifically provides a polybutylene adipate terephthalate/starch high-barrier composite film and a preparation method thereof. The film adopts a sandwich structure, and the polybutylene adipate terephthalate The butylene formate composite material is the outer layer, and the sandwich layer is a starch nanocomposite layer, and the thickness of the sandwich layer is 40%-90% of the entire composite film; the composite film with this structure has good barrier It is widely used in the packaging of easily oxidized products, especially the packaging of fresh agricultural products and high-oil foods, and at the same time significantly reduces the production cost of fully degradable packaging films.
abstract_original: 本发明涉及食品包装领域，具体提供了一种聚己二酸对苯二甲酸丁二酯/淀粉高阻隔复合膜及其制备方法，该膜采用夹心结构，所述的聚己二酸对苯二甲酸丁二酯复合材料为外层，所述的夹心层为淀粉纳米复合材料层，所述的夹心层厚度为整个复合膜的40％‑90％；采用这种结构的复合膜具有良好的阻隔性能，广泛应用于易氧化产品的包装，尤其是生鲜农产品和高油食品的包装，同时显著降低了全降解包装膜的生产成本。
claims: 4.一种聚己二酸对苯二甲酸丁二酯/淀粉高阻隔复合膜的制备方法，其特征在于：采用多层共挤流延或多层共挤吹塑的方法制备。4. A preparation method of polybutylene adipate terephthalate/starch high-barrier composite film, characterized in that: it is prepared by multi-layer co-extrusion casting or multi-layer co-extrusion blow molding.

5.根据权利要求4所述的聚己二酸对苯二甲酸丁二酯/淀粉高阻隔复合膜的制备方法，其特征在于：5. the preparation method of polybutylene adipate terephthalate/starch high barrier composite film according to claim 4, is characterized in that:
      
      
         所述的多层共挤流延是指采用两台挤出机和ABA型挤出流延模具制备三层膜，或者采用三台挤出机和ABCBA型挤出流延模具制备5层膜，然后采用三辊压光机或者双向拉伸装置处理薄膜。The multi-layer co-extrusion casting refers to adopting two extruders and an ABA type extrusion casting die to prepare a three-layer film, or adopting three extruders and an ABCBA type extrusion casting die to prepare a 5-layer film, The film is then processed using a three-roll calender or a biaxial stretching unit.

6.根据权利要求4所述的聚己二酸对苯二甲酸丁二酯/淀粉高阻隔复合膜的制备方法，其特征在于：6. the preparation method of polybutylene adipate terephthalate/starch high barrier composite film according to claim 4, is characterized in that:
      
      
         所述的多层共挤吹塑是指采用两台挤出机和ABA型吹膜机头制备三层膜，或者采用三台挤出机和ABCBA型吹膜机头制备五层膜，复合膜从吹膜机头出来后，采用两次吹泡工艺进行后处理。The multi-layer co-extrusion blow molding refers to the preparation of three-layer film by two extruders and ABA type blown film head, or the preparation of five-layer film by three extruders and ABCBA type blown film head, composite film After coming out of the film blowing machine head, it adopts two blowing processes for post-processing.

7.根据权利要求5或6所述的聚己二酸对苯二甲酸丁二酯/淀粉高阻隔复合膜的制备方法，其特征在于：7. according to the preparation method of the polybutylene adipate terephthalate/starch high barrier composite film described in claim 5 or 6, it is characterized in that:
      
      
         聚己二酸对苯二甲酸丁二酯复合材料层的挤出温度为100-180℃，淀粉纳米复合材料层的挤出温度为110-190℃，机头模具温度为150-190℃，后处理温度为70-120℃。The extrusion temperature of the polybutylene adipate terephthalate composite material layer is 100-180°C, the extrusion temperature of the starch nanocomposite layer is 110-190°C, and the die temperature of the die is 150-190°C. The treatment temperature is 70-120°C.
